  "body": "### Component\n\nAnvil\n\n### Have you ensured that all of these are up to date?\n\n- [X] Foundry\n- [X] Foundryup\n\n### What version of Foundry are you on?\n\nforge 0.2.0 (93ee742 2022-08-18T00:04:52.444331Z)\n\n### What command(s) is the bug in?\n\nanvil_reset\n\n### Operating System\n\nmacOS (Intel)\n\n### Describe the bug\n\nReset on hardhat syncs to latest block, this should be the same on anvil but it doesn't work.\r\n\r\n`{\"jsonrpc\": \"2.0\", \"method\": \"anvil_reset\", \"params\": [{\"forking\": {\"jsonRpcUrl\": \"https://NODEURL\"}}], \"id\": 1}`\r\n",
